{"tid":2164052,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"62%日本企業表示如果要中美市場二選一會選擇美國市場","createTime":"2020-08-19T04:13:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-19T04:13:24.000Z","uid":339805,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"0d1e8c9acdbf253b0793473926c86db74ee4b07e","tid":2164052,"uid":339805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T04:13:24.000Z","msg":"日經研究（Nikkei Research）於8月3日至13日為路透社進行的調查顯示，20%的日本公司正在或考慮將業務、營運基地和供應鏈遷出中國，將業務轉移到亞洲其他地區。<br />\n<br />\n62%受訪企業表示，如果不得不在中美和美國市場間作出選擇，將會選擇美國市場，而非中國市場。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e7%b6%93%e6%bf%9f/article/20200819/s00002/1597810086477\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e7%25b6%2593%25e6%25bf%259f%2Farticle%2F20200819%2Fs00002%2F1597810086477&d=MYvC0VRZm9a3oqKPvUvInAEDdXZq%2B7ycbDpBQOFx8Mg%3D&h=0f1830fb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e7%25b6%2593%25e6%25bf%259f%2Farticle%2F20200819%2Fs00002%2F1597810086477&h=93196716\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e7%b6%93%e6%bf%9f/article/20200819/s00002/1597810086477</a>"}]}